msgstr ""

#: ../../source/development/contribute-to-docs/document-style-guide/reference.rst:128
msgid "我确定这些信息是准确的，遵循术语表中的定义，没有使用模凌两可的用语；"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/development/contribute-to-docs/document-style-guide/reference.rst:129
