msgstr ""

#: ../../source/development/contribute-to-docs/document-style-guide/reference.rst:130
msgid "我确保没有做除了描述以外的事情；"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/development/contribute-to-docs/document-style-guide/reference.rst:131
msgid "我确保按照风格指南进行描述，整个参考页面和其它参考页面的风格是一致的。"
msgstr ""

